orkers%2C%20vowed%20to%20reward%20top%20performers%20and%20swiftly%20address%20under-performers.%20That%20mirrors%20Musk's%20midnight%20missive%20to%20Twitter%20staff%2C%20which%20demanded%20%26quot%3Bexceptional%20performance%26quot%3B%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bonly%20passing%20grade%26quot%3B%20and%20presaged%20job%20cuts%20that%20eliminated%20about%2080%25%20of%20the%20company's%20workforce.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOPM%20also%20promised%20a%20leaner%20workforce%2C%20noting%20that%20while%20defense%20and%20security%20agencies%20may%20grow%2C%20most%20federal%20departments%20will%20face%20downsizing%20through%20layoffs%2C%20furloughs%2C%20and%20reclassifying%20roles%20as%20%26quot%3Bat-will%26quot%3B%20employment%2C%20eroding%20civil-service%20protections%20that%20have%20shielded%20workers%20for%20decades.%20Federal%20employees%20must%20also%20meet%20heightened%20standards%20of%20reliability%2C%20loyalty%2C%20and%20trustworthiness%2C%20according%20to%20the%20OPM.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20blueprint%20echoes%20Elon%20Musk's%20rapid-fire%20restructuring%20of%20Twitter.%20Soon%20after%20acquiring%20the%20platform%2C%20Musk%20told%20employees%20they%20had%2040%20hours%20to%20commit%20to%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3Eextremely%20hardcore%3Cem%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20work%20environment%20or%20accept%20severance.%20More%20than%206%2C000%20Twitter%20staff%20eventually%20left%20or%20were%20laid%20off%2C%20including%20engineers%20and%20content%20moderators.%20Musk%20also%20issued%20RTO%20mandates.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e59d072d-2aab-4345-ab52-58dec264f828%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ERisks%20and%20rising%20debt%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20risks%20of%20Musk's%20approach%20are%20well-documented.%20Twitter's%20user%20growth%20stalled%20post-takeover%2C%20and%20its%20brand%20reputation%20tanked%20as%20advertisers%20fled%20after%20controversial%20policy%20shifts.%20%3C%2Fs