has%20piled%20up%20since%202017%2C%20according%20to%20Treasury%20Department%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffiscaldata.treasury.gov%2Famericas-finance-guide%2Fnational-debt%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cu%3Edata%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERising%20rates%20have%20increased%20the%20cost%20of%20paying%20interest%20on%20this%20massive%20debt%20load.%20In%202023%2C%20these%20annual%20payments%20topped%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fbonds%2Fus-debt-interest-payments-federal-deficit-treasury-bonds-fed-hikes-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cu%3E%241%20trillion%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20stoking%20concern%20among%20some%20economists%20about%20government%20spending.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20partly%20what's%20driving%20the%20Trump%20administration%20to%20try%20to%20make%20the%20US%20government%20more%20efficient.%20Trump%20has%20also%20pledged%20to%20pursue%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-pay-in-taxes-trump-tax-bill-expiring-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cu%3Etax%20cuts%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20putting%20even%20more%20pressure%20on%20his%20administration%20to%20find%20other%20ways%20of%20controlling%20the%20ballooning%20national%20debt.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETrump's%20efficiency%20drive%20has%20already%20caused%20turmoil.%20Some%20government%20workers%20said%20his%20federal%20grant%20freeze%20has%20thrown%20agencies%20into%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffederal-workers-react-trump-federal-funding-freeze-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cu%3Edisarray%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20creating%20confusion.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20Musk%20eliminated%20thousands%20of%20Twitter%20jobs%2C%20some%20employees%20at%20the%20company%20were%20concerned%20that%20the%20social-media%20platform%20might%20stop%20working%20because%20the%20cuts%20were%20so%20deep%20and%20fast.%20There%20were%20some%20outages%2C%20but%20the%20company's%20technical%20underpinnings%20have%20been%20running%20relatively%20smoothly%20over%20the%20past%20year%20or%20so.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-buyout-offer-government-workers-elon-musk-twitter-layoff-strategy-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738119556000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6799960d196626c4098592fe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-buyout-offer-government-workers-elon-musk-twitter-layoff-strategy-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20new%20administration%20is%20emailing%20government%20employees%20draft%20resignation%20letters.%20Musk%20sent%20a%20similar%20email%20to%20Twitter%20staff%20in%202022.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22pdixit%40insider.com%20(Pranav%20Dixit)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-buyout-offer-government-workers-elon-musk-twitter-layoff-strategy-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ISRO%20Hits%20100th%20Rocket%20Launch%20Milestone%20With%20Navigation%20Sat%20Mission%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%20successfully%20launched%20their%20GSLV-F15%20carrying%20the%20NVS-02%20on%206%3A23%20AM%20at%20Sriharikota%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20marking%20ISRO's%20100th%20rocket%20mission.%20The%20mission%20is%20also%20the%20first%20for%20the%20space%20agency's%20Chairman%20V%20Narayanan%2C%20who%20assumed%20office%20recently.%20It%20is%20ISRO's%20maiden%20venture%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20satellite%20was%20%26quot%3Bprecisely%20injected%20into%20the%20required%20(GTO)%20orbit.%20This%20mission%20is%20the%20100th%20launch%20which%20is%20a%20very%20significant%20milestone%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Narayanan%20said%20in%20his%20address%20post%20the%20successful%20launch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20this%20mission%2C%20the%20data%20has%20come%3B%20all%20vehicle%20systems%20are%20normal%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20big%20rocket%20to%20liftoff%20from%20Sriharikota%20was%20the%20Satellite%20Launch%20Vehicle%20(SLV)%20on%20August%2010%2C%201979%2C%20and%20now%20nearly%2046%20years%20later%20the%20Department%20of%20Space%20has%20hit%20a%20century.%20Till%20now%20all%20big%20rocket%20launches%20at%20Sriharikota%20have%20been%20by%20the%20Indian%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20S.%20Unnikrishnan%20Nair%2C%20Director%20of%20India's%20main%20rocket%20lab%20the%20Vikram%20Sarabhai%20Space%20Center%2C%20in%20Thiruvananthapuram%20said%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20as%20robust%20as%20previous%20one.%20Like%20any%20other%20launch.%20We%20make%20every%20launch%20robust%20to%20the%20best%20of%20our%20ability.%20It%20will%20be%20successful.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20rocket%20was%20once%20dubbed%20as%20the%20'naughty%20boy'%20of%20ISRO%20since%20it%20gave%20the%20Indian%20space%20agency%20the%20worst%20time%20of%20all%20its%20menagerie%20of%20rockets.%20Since%20out%20of%2016%20launches%20so%20far%20there%20have%20been%206%20failures%20for%20this%20rocket%2C%20which%20is%20a%20huge%2037%25%20failure%20rate.%20In%20comparison%20India's%20latest%20the%20Bahuballi%20rocket%20the%20Launch%20Vehicle%20Mark%20-3%20has%20a%20one%20hundred%20percent%20success%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20a%20rocket%20from%20the%20same%20family%20where%20India%20showed%20its%20innate%20skill%20of%20mastering%20the%20making%20of%20cryogenic%20engines%2C%20a%20technology%20the%20country%20took%20two%20decades%20to%20master%20after%20the%20technology%20transfer%20of%20the%20same%20was%20denied%20to%20India%2C%20by%20Russia%20under%20pressure%20from%20USA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EISRO%20states%20GSLV-F15%20is%20the%2017th%20flight%20of%20India's%20Geosynchronous%20Satellite%20Launch%20Vehicle%20(GSLV)%20and%2011th%20flight%20with%20indigenous%20cryogenic%20stage.%20It%20is%20the%208th%20operational%20flight%20of%20GSLV%20with%20an%20indigenous%20cryogenic%20stage%20and%20100th%20Launch%20from%20the%20India's%20Spaceport%20Sriharikota.%20GSLV-F15%20payload%20fairing%20is%20a%20metallic%20version%20with%20a%20diameter%20of%203.4%20meters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20GSLV-F15%20with%20indigenous%20Cryogenic%20stage%20will%20place%20NVS-02%20satellite%20into%20a%20Geosynchronous%20Transfer%20Orbit%20%26amp%3B%20the%20launch%20will%20take%20place%20from%20the%20Second%20Launch%20Pad%20(SLP)%20at%20Satish%20Dhawan%20Space%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENavigation%20with%20Indian%20Constellation%20(NavIC)%20is%20India's%20independent%20regional%20navigation%20satellite%20system%20designed%20to%20provide%20accurate%20Position%2C%20Velocity%20and%20Timing%20(PVT)%20service%20to%20users%20in%20India%20as%20well%20as%20to%20region%20extending%20about%201500%20km%20beyond%20Indian%20land%20mass.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENavIC%20will%20provide%20two%20types%20of%20services%2C%20namely%2C%20Standard%20Positioning%20Service%20(SPS)%20and%20Restricted%20Service%20(RS).%20NavIC's%20SPS%20provides%20a%20position%20accuracy%20of%20better%20than%2020%20meters%20and%20timing%20accuracy%20better%20than%2040%20nano%20seconds%20over%20the%20service%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENavIC%20has%20given%20India%20its%20own%20share%20of%20challenges%2C%20since%20it%20was%20born%20out%20of%20the%20very%20bad%20experience%20the%20country%20had%20after%20the%201999%20skirmish%20with%20Pakistan%20at%20Kargil%2C%20in%20that%20conflict%20India%20was%20denied%20access%20to%20high%20quality%20Global%20Positioning%20System%20(GPS)%20data%20and%20the%20then%20Prime%20Minister%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20promised%20to%20make%20a%20swadeshi%20version%20of%20the%20GPS%20for%20India's%20strategic%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20on%20this%20hundredth%20launch%20ISRO%20hopes%20that%20the%20early%20challenges%20posed%20by%20the%20navigation%20satellites%20and%20the%20rocket%20are%20a%20thing%20of%20the%20past%20and%20it%20hopes%20to%20hit%20the%20hundredth%20mark%20in%20style.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738119540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fumht1td8_isro-gslvf15-launch_625x300_29_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-isros-100th-mission-gslv-f15-carrying-navigation-satellite-lifts-off-7583314%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%20successfully%20launched%20their%20GSLV-F15%20carrying%20the%20NVS-02%20on%206%3A23%20AM%20at%20Sriharikota%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20marking%20ISRO's%20100th%20rocket%20mission.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ICC%20CEO%20steps%20down%2C%20Champions%20Trophy%20preparations%20in%20Pakistan%20questioned%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738119396000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117664974%2Cimgsize-32456.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Ficc-ceo-steps-down-champions-trophy-preparations-in-pakistan-questioned%2Farticleshow%2F117665074.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22ICC%20CEO%20Geoff%20Allardice%20resigned%20shortly%20before%20the%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%20amid%20scrutiny%20over%20mishandled%20funds%20and%20unprepared%20venues%20in%20Pakistan.%20The%20ICC%20board%20was%20dissatisfied%20with%20the%20progress%20of%20the%20stadiums.%20ICC%20chairman%20Jay%20Shah%20confirmed%20th