red%20when%20a%20stampede-like%20situation%20unfolded%20at%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20Mauni%20Amavasya%2C%20prompting%20Akharas%20to%20call%20off%20the%20holy%20dip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20crores%20of%20devotees%20streamed%20into%20the%20tent%20city%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Prayagraj%20ahead%20of%20the%20'Amrit%20Snan'.%20Amid%20a%20surge%20in%20crowd%20about%20a%20kilometre%20away%20from%20the%20'Sangam'%2C%20barricades%20broke%20leading%20some%20women%20to%20faint.%20As%20the%20unconscious%20women%20fell%2C%20the%20stampede-like%20situation%20began.%20They%20were%20then%20rushed%20to%20a%20hospital%20within%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%20fair%20grounds.%20Further%2C%20some%20seriously%20injured%20women%20were%20sent%20to%20Bailey%20Hospital%20and%20Swaroop%20Rani%20Medical%20College%20or%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkhil%20Bharatiya%20Akhara%20Parishad%20president%20Mahant%20Ravindra%20Puri%20said%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaha-kumbh-mela-prayagraj-2025-akharas-call-off-mauni-amavasya-amrit-snan-after-stampede-like-situation-7583378%5C%22%3Eseers%20have%20called%20off%3C%2Fa%3E%20their%20Mauni%20Amavasya's%20Amrit%20Snan.%20%26quot%3BYou%20would've%20seen%20what%20happened%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20and%20that's%20why%20we%20have%20decided%20to...%20All%20of%20our%20saints%20and%20seers%20were%20ready%20for%20the%20'snan'%20when%20we%20were%20informed%20about%20this%20incident.%20That's%20why%20we%20have%20decided%20to%20call%20off%20our%20'snan'%20on%20'Mauni%20Amavasya'%2C%26quot%3B%20Mahant%20Ravindra%20Puri%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaha-kumbh-2025-live-updates-pm-modi-dials-yogi-adityanath-after-stampede-like-situation-in-prayagraj-7583377%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFollow%20Live%20Updates%20From%20Maha%20Kumbh%202025%20Here%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkhada%20Parishad%20General%20Secretary%20and%20Juna%20Akhara%20Patron%20Mahant%20Hari%20Giri%20too%20appealed%20to%20devotees%20to%20take%20a%20bath%20in%20the%20Ganga%20river%20wherever%20they%20are%20and%20return%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20spoke%20to%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20and%20directed%20him%20to%20arrange%20immediate%20relief%20measures.%20Authorities%20closed%20pontoon%20bridges%20to%20avoid%20similar%20situations%20at%20other%20places%20within%20the%20fair%20grounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20ahead%20of%20the%20second%20Amrit%20Snan%2C%20nearly%20five%20crore%20people%20had%20already%20reached%20Prayagraj%2C%20while%20crowds%20were%20pegged%20to%20swell%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famrit-snan-10-crore-pilgrims-likely-to-take-holy-dip-at-maha-kumbh-tomorrow-7576939%5C%22%3E10%20crore%20on%20the%20day%20itself%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Authorities%20implemented%20stringent%20security%20measures%2C%20managing%20massive%20crowds%20with%20AI-powered%20surveillance%2C%20drone%20monitoring%2C%20and%20increased%20police%20presence.%20While%20the%20Mela%20area%20has%20already%20been%20declared%20a%20no-vehicle%20zone%20for%20the%20next%20few%20days%2C%20the%20Prayagraj%20administration%20has%20also%20made%20a%20fervent%20appeal%20to%20local%20residents%20to%20avoid%20using%20four%20wheelers%20and%20opt%20for%20two%20wheelers%20only%20if%20carrying%20senior%20citizens%20to%20the%20Sangam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaha-kumbh-railways-running-360-trains-in-prayagraj-on-mauni-amavasya-7581842%5C%22%3Erailways%20is%20running%20360%20trains%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20190%20special%20trains%2C%20to%20accommodate%20the%20unprecedented%20influx%20of%20pilgrims.%20%26quot%3BThe%20special%20trains%20are%20being%20run%20in%20three%20zones%20--%20Northern%20Railway%2C%20North%20Eastern%20Railway%20and%20North%20Central%20Railway%20--%20to%20manage%20the%20massive%20influx%20of%20devotees%2C%26quot%3B%20Satish%20Kumar%2C%20Chairman%20and%20CEO%20of%20the%20Railway%20Board%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20historic%20move%20will%20ensure%20a%20train%20runs%20every%20four%20minutes%2C%20and%20provide%20seamless%20connectivity%20and%20uninterrupted%20travel%20for%20millions%20of%20pilgrims%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmahakumbh-passengers-throw-stones-at-mahakumbh-special-train-on-finding-doors-locked-7576143%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPassengers%20Throw%20Stones%20At%20Mahakumbh%20Special%20Train%20On%20Finding%20Doors%20Locked%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20has%20deployed%20more%20than%201%2C000%20medical%20professionals%20in%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%20area%2C%20apart%20from%20provisions%20for%20minor%20to%20major%20surgeries%20in%20every%20sector%20of%20the%20fair%20area%2C%20an%20official%20statement%20said.%20Additionally%2C%20300%20specialist%20doctors%20are%20stationed%20at%20a%20super-specialty%20hospital%20in%20the%20Mahakumbh%20Nagar%20to%20handle%20any%20emergency%20situations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Amrit%20Snan%20on%20Mauni%20Amavasya%20is%20the%20most%20significant%20ritual%20of%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh.%20This%20year%2C%20the%20occasion%20holds%20added%20spiritual%20importance%20due%20to%20a%20rare%20celestial%20alignment%20known%20as%20'Triveni%20Yog%2C'%20which%20occurs%20once%20every%20144%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20tradition%20of%20the%20Kumbh%20Mela%2C%20Akharas%20belonging%20to%20the%20three%20sects%20'Sanyasi%2C%20Bairagi%2C%20and%20Udaseen'%20take%20the%20holy%20dip%20in%20a%20set%20sequence%20following%20a%20majestic%2C%20awe-inspiring%20procession%20to%20the%20Sangam%20Ghat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seers%20and%20saints%2C%20including%20the%20ash-smeared%20Nagas%2C%20then%20immerse%20themselves%20in%20the%20sacred%20confluence%20of%20the%20Ganga%2C%20Yamuna%2C%20and%20mythical%20Saraswati%20rivers%20on%20special%20bathing%20dates%20like%20the%20Mauni%20Amavasya.%20Mauni%20Amavasya%20is%20considered%20the%20most%20auspicious%20date%20among%20all%20the%20special%20bathing%20dates%2C%20and%20it%20is%20believed%20that%20on%20this%20day%2C%20the%20water%20of%20the%20holy%20rivers%20turns%20into%20'Amrit.'%20The%20government%20also%20planned%20to%20shower%2025%20quintals%20of%20rose%20petals%20using%20helicopters%20on%20the%20devotees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-16-days-record-23-9-million-devotees-took-holy-dip-at-maha-kumbh-7581886%5C%22%3EMaha%20Kumbh%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20already%20witnessed%20over%2015%20crore%20pilgrims%20taking%20a%20holy%20dip%20in%20the%20past%2017%20days.%20Over%204.80%20crore%20devotees%20took%20the%20snan%20on%20Tuesday%20alone%20-%20even%20more%20than%20that%20of%20Amrit%20Snan'%20on%20Makar%20Sankranti%20(3.5%20crore)%2C%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maha%20Kumbh%20started%20on%20January%2013%20and%20will%20continue%20till%20February%2026.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738118640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftvdata.s2.apps.ndtv.com%2Fdata%2Fimages%2FPTI01_29_2025_000008B.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fstampede-like-situation-at-maha-kumbh-on-mauni-amavasya-many-feared-injured-7583118%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Around%2030%20women%20were%20injured%20when%20a%20stampede-like%20situation%20unfolded%20at%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20Mauni%20Amavasya%2C%20prompting%20Akharas%20to%20call%20off%20the%20holy%20dip.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Birthright%20citizenship%20is%20unconstitutional'%3A%20White%20House%20press%20secretary%20Karoline%20Leavitt%20in%20her%20first%20briefing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738118611