e-temporarily-froze-all-federal-grants-and-loans-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esuspended%20federal%20grants%20and%20loans%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20federal%20judge%20temporarily%20blocked%20the%20funding%20freeze%20right%20before%20it%20was%20set%20to%20go%20into%20effect%20on%20Tuesday%20evening%2C%20the%20Associated%20Press%20reported.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Office%20of%20Management%20and%20Budget's%20internal%20memo%20sent%20Monday%20night%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhite-house-temporarily-froze-all-federal-grants-and-loans-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eobtained%20by%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eagencies%20must%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-omb-federal-grant-pause-history-impoundment-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epause%20any%20payments%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20programs%20that%20include%20%26quot%3Bfinancial%20assistance%20for%20foreign%20aid%2C%20nongovernmental%20organizations%2C%20DEI%2C%20woke%20gender%20ideology%2C%20and%20the%20green%20new%20deal%2C%26quot%3B%20suggesting%20the%20administration%20is%20looking%20to%20pause%20programs%20that%20are%20not%20in%20line%20with%20Trump's%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20carved%20out%20exceptions%20for%20%26quot%3Bassistance%20provided%20directly%20to%20individuals%26quot%3B%20and%20would%20not%20impact%20Medicare%20or%20Social%20Security%20benefits.%20Still%2C%20the%20order's%20lack%20of%20clarity%20has%20some%20groups%20that%20receive%20federal%20aid%20struggling%20to%20determine%20how%20they%20will%20be%20impacted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20Tuesday%20afternoon%2C%20BI%20reporters%20had%20contacted%20more%20than%2060%20federal%2C%20state%2C%20and%20nonprofit%20agencies.%20Those%20who%20responded%20overwhelmingly%20said%20they%20had%20no%20idea%20how%20the%20federal%20funding%20freeze%20would%20affect%20their%20work%20and%20were%20actively%20trying%20to%20figure%20it%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20administration%20official%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20pause%20on%20federal%20grants%20is%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20law%20and%20will%20not%20impact%20benefits%20provided%20directly%20to%20Americans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Meals%20on%20Wheels%2C%20which%20receives%20federal%20grants%20to%20provide%20meals%20to%20seniors%2C%20told%20BI%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20lack%20of%20clarity%20and%20uncertainty%20right%20now%20is%20creating%20chaos%20for%20local%20Meals%20on%20Wheels%20providers%20not%20knowing%20whether%20they're%20going%20to%20be%20reimbursed%20for%20meals%20served%20today%2C%20tomorrow%2C%20who%20knows%20how%20long%20this%20could%20go%20on.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESenator%20Chris%20Murphy%20of%20Connecticut%20wrote%20on%20X%20Tuesday%20afternoon%20that%20his%20state's%20Head%20Start%20reimbursement%20system%20was%20shut%20down.%20%26quot%3BPreschools%20cannot%20pay%20staff%20and%20will%20need%20to%20start%20laying%20off%20staff%20very%20soon%20and%20sending%20little%20kids%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20Head%20Start's%20office%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20BI's%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pause%20was%20set%20to%20begin%20on%20Tuesday%20at%205%20p.m.%20ET%2C%20leaving%20some%20organizations%20that%20receive%20federal%20aid%20scrambling%20to%20determine%20how%20to%20account%20for%20this%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2250b7da78-2aa1-4339-9574-ebaf1c810759%5C%22%3EWhich%20programs%20could%20be%20most%20at%20risk%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20order%20seems%20to%20clearly%20target%20funding%20for%20programs%20that%20could%20fall%20under%20a%20broad%20DEI%20or%20renewable%20energy%20umbrella%2C%20implications%20for%20other%20groups%20are%20much%20less%20clear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDepending%20on%20how%20long%20the%20freeze%20on%20federal%20grants%20and%20loans%20last%2C%20some%20programs%20could%20be%20impacted%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20days.%20Bobby%20Kogan%2C%20senior%20director%20of%20federal%20budget%20policy%20at%20the%20left-leaning%20think-tank%20Center%20for%20American%20Progress%2C%20highlighted%20two%20programs%3A%20Head%20Start%2C%20which%20receives%20federal%20funding%20to%20help%20low-income%20children%20and%20families%20receive%20aid%20for%20early%20childhood%20education%2C%20and%20Section%208%2C%20which%20provides%20housing%20vouchers%20for%20low-income%20individuals%20and%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHead%20Start%20receives%20its%20funding%20through%20annual%20contracts%20on%20a%20rolling%20basis%2C%20so%20the%20grant%20freeze%20would%20delay%20payments%20for%20facilities%20that%20were%20expected%20to%20get%20funding%20on%20February%201.%20Additionally%2C%20Section%208%20vouchers%20are%20distributed%20to%20housing%20authorities%2C%20and%20those%20who%20do%20not%20have%20cash%20reserves%20may%20be%20unable%20to%20help%20voucher%20recipients%20with%20their%20rent%20on%20February%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20impacts%20are%20immediate%2C%20and%20some%20are%20not%20immediate%2C%20but%20the%20longer%20that%20it%20goes%20on%2C%20the%20more%20things%20are%20impacted%2C%26quot%3B%20Kogan%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20obtained%20a%20memo%20OMB%20sent%20to%20federal%20agencies%20requesting%20they%20complete%20a%20spreadsheet%20detailing%20the%20objectives%20and%20funding%20schedules%20of%20federal%20programs%20they%20oversee.%20Those%20programs%20included%20SNAP%2C%20WIC%2C%20and%20aid%20for%20homeless%20veterans%2C%20among%20other%20things.%20It's%20unclear%20how%20OMB%20will%20use%20that%20information%2C%20especially%20because%20a%20senior%20administration%20official%20said%20SNAP%20would%20be%20exempt%20from%20the%20freeze.%20But%20the%20items%20on%20the%20list%20could%20signal%20programs%20Trump's%20administration%20is%20looking%20to%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESharron%20Parrott%2C%20president%20of%20the%20left-leaning%20Center%20on%20Budget%20and%20Policy%20Priorities%2C%20compared%20the%20grants%20pause%20to%20a%20government%20shutdown%20%E2%80%94%20but%20she%20said%20that%20the%20preparation%20that%20typically%20goes%20into%20a%20shutdown%20is%20missing%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20terrible%20thing%20when%20the%20government%20shuts%20down%2C%20and%20lots%20of%20people%20are%20hurt%20in%20a%20whole%20variety%20of%20ways%2C%20but%20that%20careful%20preparation%2C%20that%20figuring%20out%20what%20needs%20to%20continue%20to%20preserve%20life%20and%20safety%2C%20is%20incredibly%20important%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20completely%20absent%20from%20this%20chaotic%20process.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20Democratic%20lawmakers%20have%20also%20highlighted%20potential%20programs%20at%20risk%20under%20a%20hiring%20freeze.%20Sen.%20Bernie%20Sanders%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20the%20memo%20has%20sparked%20confusion%20over%20the%20fate%20of%20Head%20Start%2C%20nutritional%20assistance%20for%20pregnant%20mothers%20through%20the%20WIC%20program%2C%20and%20heating%20for%20low-income%20Americans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Trump%20Administration's%20action%20last%20night%20to%20suspend%20all%20federal%20grants%20and%20loans%20will%20have%20a%20devastating%20impact%20on%20the%20health%20and%20well-being%20of%20millions%20of%20children%2C%20seniors%20on%20fixed%20incomes%2C%20and%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20people%20in%20our%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20Sanders%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20freeze%20on%20grants%20and%20loans%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flawsuits-challenge-trump-over-freeze-federal-loans-grants-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealready%20facing%20legal%20challenges%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20well%20%E2%80%94%20a%20group%20of%20state%20attorneys%20general%20said%20they%20would%20sue%20to%20stop%20the%20freeze%2C%20and%20a%20group%20of%20nonprofits%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20on%20Tuesday%20to%20prevent%20it%20from%20going%20into%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%