0The%20Beatles%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20a%20complete%20timeline%20of%20Drake's%20major%20life%20events%20and%20his%20rise%20to%20global%20stardom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22818349d4-06c2-4d72-802d-f60b01eddf32%5C%22%3EAubrey%20Drake%20Graham%20was%20born%20on%20October%2024%2C%201986.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22drake%20parents%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5bcf58c7c7621906a2645af3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDrake's%20father%20is%20from%20Memphis%2C%20Tennessee%2C%20while%20his%20mother%20is%20Canadian.%3Cp%3E%40champagnepapi%2FInstagram%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDrake's%20parents%20divorced%20when%20he%20was%205.%20His%20father%2C%20Dennis%20Graham%2C%20is%20Black%20and%20Catholic%3B%20his%20mother%2C%20Sandra%2C%20is%20white%20and%20Ashkenazi%20Jewish%20Canadian.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%C2%A0have%20a%20very%20deep%20musical%20background.%20My%20grandmother%2C%20who%20passed%20away%20in%20Memphis%2C%20used%20to%20babysit%20Louis%20Armstrong.%20And%20my%20dad%20was%20a%20drummer%20for%20Jerry%20Lee%20Lewis%2C%26quot%3B%20Drake%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20061022074910%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.hiphopcanada.com%2F_site%2Fentertainment%2Finterviews%2Fent_int314.php%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHip%20Hop%20Canada%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202006.%20%26quot%3BOn%20my%20mom's%20side%2C%20it's%20a%20white%2C%20Jewish%2C%20very%20structured%20and%20conservative%20family.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20accolades%20on%20that%20side%20of%20the%20family%20too%2C%26quot%3B%C2%A0he%20added.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20aware%20that%20I%20am%20not%20the%20first%20person%20%5Bin%20the%20family%20to%20embrace%20music%5D%20but%20I%20would%20like%20to%20become%20the%20first%20one%20to%20be%20an%20icon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDrake