20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F117651478.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EJunaid%20Khan%20admitted%20that%20his%20playful%20comment%20about%20his%20father%20Aamir%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20personal%20life%20during%20the%20Bigg%20Boss%2018%20grand%20finale%20was%20out%20of%20place.%20Reflecting%20on%20the%20incident%2C%20Junaid%20expressed%20regret%2C%20acknowledging%20that%20he%20could%20have%20acted%20more%20appropriately%20given%20the%20stature%20of%20the%20personalities%20involved.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fjunaid-khan-regrets-his-playful-comment-on-dad-aamir-khans-ex-wives-on-bigg-boss-18-finale-with-salman-khan-i-should-have-behaved%2Farticleshow%2F117651478.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Parliament%20Panel%20On%20Waqf%20Circulates%20Draft%20Report.%20Opposition%20Says%20%26quot%3BFarce%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20parliamentary%20panel%20reviewing%20the%20Waqf%20bill%20circulated%20a%20655-page%20report%20today%2C%20incorporating%20all%20the%20changes%20suggested%20by%20its%20members.%20The%20Opposition%2C%20though%2C%20has%20alleged%20that%20none%20of%20its%20amendments%20have%20been%20incorporated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20fears%20that%20the%20existing%20Waqf%20properties%20will%20be%20subject%20to%20scrutiny%20after%20the%20amended%20law%20comes%20into%20force%2C%20the%20committee%20has%20recommended%20that%20no%20cases%20will%20be%20reopened%20against%20such%20properties%20on%20a%20retrospective%20basis%2C%20provided%20the%20asset%20is%20not%20in%20dispute%20or%20belongs%20to%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20has%20accepted%2014%20amendments%2C%20which%20have%20been%20suggested%20by%20members%20of%20the%20BJP%20or%20its%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20proposes%20numerous%20changes%20to%20the%20way%20Waqf%20boards%20are%20administered%2C%20including%20nominating%20non-Muslim%20and%20(at%20least%20two)%20women%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20also%20has%20a%20provision%20that%20says%20the%20central%20Waqf%20Council%20must%20include%20a%20union%20minister%20and%20three%20MPs%2C%20two%20ex-judges%2C%20four%20people%20of%20'national%20repute'%2C%20and%20senior%20government%20officials%2C%20none%20of%20whom%20need%20be%20from%20the%20Islamic%20faith.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20under%20the%20new%20rules%20the%20Waqf%20Council%20can't%20claim%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20leaders%20have%20also%20criticised%20the%20committee%20alleging%20a%20very%20short%20time%20has%20been%20allowed%20for%20studying%20the%20draft%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20chaired%20by%20BJP%20leader%20Jagdambika%20Pal%20is%20expected%20to%20adopt%20the%20report%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20parliamentary%20committee%20on%20Waqf%20Bill%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20a%20farce.%20We%20were%20told%20that%20the%20draft%20report%20of%20the%20committee%20and%20its%20bill%20will%20be%20discussed%20tomorrow%20at%2010%20am.%20It%20is%20a%20655-page%20report%20which%20has%20been%20sent%20to%20us%20just%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20DMK%20leader%20A%20Raja.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Raja%20said%20the%20MPs%20are%20expected%20to%20go%20through%20it%2C%20provide%20comments%20and%20submit%20dissent%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20simply%20not%20possible.%20What%20is%20the%20point%20of%20an%20independent%20parliamentary%20committee%20if%20the%20government%20does%20as%20it%20pleases%20anyway%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20Union%20minister%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKey%20Provisions%20of%20the%20Waqf%20Amendment%20Bill%2C%202025%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETwo%20Muslim%20women%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20included%20as%20members%20in%20both%20the%20State%20Waqf%20Boards%20(Section%2014)%20and%20the%20Central%20Waqf%20Council%20(Section%209)%20to%20ensure%20Muslim%20women's%20empowerment%20and%20participation%20in%20waqf%20management.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%20The%20State%20Waqf%20Boards%20will%20now%20include%20one%20member%20from%20the%20Muslim%20OBC%20community%2C%20ensuring%20broader%20representation%20(Section%2014).%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%20The%20State%20Government%20may%20establish%20separate%20Waqf%20Boards%20for%20Aghakhani%20and%20Bohra%20communities%2C%20acknowledging%20their%20distinct%20religious%20needs%20(Section%2013).%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%20In%20Waqf%20Alal%20Aulad%20(family%20waqfs)%2C%20women's%20inheritance%20rights%20will%20be%20safeguarded.%20A%20waqif%20can%20dedicate%20property%20only%20after%20ensuring%20that%20female%20heirs%20receive%20their%20rightful%20share%20(Section%203A(2)).%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%20Registered%20Waqf%20by%20User%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20recognized%20as%20waqf%2C%20except%20in%20cases%20where%20the%20property%20is%20under%20dispute%20or%20owned%20by%20the%20government%20(Section%203(r)).%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0The%20Limitation%20Act%20will%20apply%20to%20all%20waqf-related%20cases%20from%20the%20commencement%20of%20this%20Act%2C%20ensuring%20timely%20resolution%20and%20preventing%20prolonged%20litigation%20(Section%20107).%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0The%20online%20registration%20process%20will%20be%20introduced%20to%20automate%20the%20entire%20life%20cycle%20of%20waqf%20properties%20through%20the%20portal.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%20Waqf%20Boards%20must%20upload%20all%20waqf%20property%20details%20on%20a%20central%20portal%20within%20six%20months.%20The%20Waqf%20Tribunal%20may%20grant%20extensions%20on%20a%20case-by-case%20basis.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%20If%20a%20government%20property%20is%20claimed%20as%20waqf%2C%20an%20officer%20above%20the%20rank%20of%20Collector%2C%20notified%20by%20the%20State%20Government%2C%20will%20conduct%20an%20inquiry%20as%20per%20the%20law.%20Until%20the%20report%20is%20submitted%2C%20such%20government%20properties%20will%20not%20be%20treated%20as%20waqf%20(Section%203C).%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0Muslim%20trusts%20that%20function%20similarly%20to%20waqf%20but%20are%20governed%20by%20trust%20laws%20will%20be%20excluded%20from%20the%20Waqf%20Act%2C%201995%2C%20preventing%20legal%20conflicts%20(Section%202A).%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0The%20income%20from%20Waqf%20Alal%20Aulad%20can%20be%20used%20to%20support%20widows%2C%20divorced%20women%2C%20and%20orphans%2C%20if%20specified%20by%20the%20waqif%20(Section%203(r)(iv)).%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0The%20finality%20of%20tribunal%20decisions%20has%20been%20removed.%20Any%20aggrieved%20person%20can%20now%20appeal%20to%20the%20High%20Court%20within%20ninety%20days%20of%20the%20tribunal's%20decision.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0Online%20registration%20certificates%20of%20waqf%20properties%20will%20be%20issued%20through%20the%20portal.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738088820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F8c57oo88_jpc-meeting-ians_625x300_28_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparliament-panel-on-waqf-circulates-draft-report-opposition-says-farce-7581957%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20parliamentary%20panel%20reviewing%20the%20Waqf%20bill%20circulated%20a%20655-page%20report%20today%2C%20incorporating%20all%20the%20changes%20suggested%20by%20its%20members.%20The%20Opposition%2C%20though%2C%20has%20alleged%20that%20none%20of%20its%20amendments%20have%20been%20incorporated.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparliament-panel-on-waqf-circulates-draft-report-opposition-says-farce-7581957%22%2C%2