essible%20compared%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20museum%26quot%3B%2C%20with%20%26quot%3Bits%20own%20access%20pass%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20museum%20in%20central%20Paris%20would%20also%20have%20a%20%26quot%3Bnew%20grand%20entrance%26quot%3B%20to%20help%20ease%20congestion%20at%20its%20glass-and-metal%20pyramid%20entry%20point%20and%20be%20financed%20entirely%20using%20the%20institution's%20%26quot%3Bown%20resources%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20so-called%20%26quot%3BNew%20Renaissance%26quot%3B%20project%2C%20France%20would%20over%20the%20next%20few%20months%20launch%20an%20%26quot%3Binternational%20architecture%20competition%26quot%3B%20and%20select%20winners%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%20to%20transform%20its%20buildings%20by%202031%20at%20the%20latest%2C%20Macron%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seat%20of%20French%20kings%20until%20Louis%20XIV%20abandoned%20it%20for%20Versailles%20in%20the%20late%201600s%2C%20the%20Louvre%20is%20regularly%20listed%20as%20the%20world's%20most%20visited%20museum%2C%20and%20houses%20masterpieces%20including%20the%20Mona%20Lisa%20and%20the%20Greek%20marble%20sculpture%20of%20Venus%20de%20Milo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Paris%20landmark%20has%20become%20a%20subject%20of%20national%20concern%20after%20the%20revelation%20last%20week%20of%20a%20confidential%20memo%20written%20by%20its%20director%20Laurence%20des%20Cars%20to%20Culture%20Minister%20Rachida%20Dati%20warning%20about%20the%20%26quot%3Bproliferation%20of%20damage%20in%20museum%20spaces%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20areas%20%26quot%3Bare%20no%20longer%20watertight%2C%20while%20others%20experience%20significant%20temperature%20variations%2C%20endangering%20the%20preservation%20of%20artworks%26quot%3B%2C%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Louvre's%20popularity%20is%20causing%20also%20a%20%26quot%3Bphysical%20strain%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20historic%20building%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDes%20Cars%20said%20the%20Louvre%20required%20an%20overhaul%20that%20was%20likely%20to%20be%20costly%20and%20technically%20complicated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%208.7%20million%20people%20visited%20its%20famed%20galleries%20last%20year%20--%20around%20twice%20the%20number%20it%20was%20designed%20for%20--%20and%20des%20Cars%20has%20expressed%20concern%20about%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20user%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20'Higher%20fee'%20for%20non-EU%20visitors%20-%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Louvre%20management%20estimates%20the%20renovation%20work%20could%20cost%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20euros.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMacron%20said%20%26quot%3Ba%20different%2C%20higher%20fee%20for%20foreign%20visitors%20from%20countries%20outside%20the%20European%20Union%26quot%3B%20starting%20next%20year%20would%20help%20cover%20the%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20government%20source%20said%20earlier%20that%20authorities%20were%20also%20considering%20ways%20to%20%26quot%3Bmobilise%20resources%20elsewhere%26quot%3B%20and%20get%20private%20donors%20and%20major%20companies%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrance%20relied%20on%20donations%20from%20billionaires%20and%20the%20public%20to%20restore%20Notre%20Dame%20cathedral%2C%20which%20was%20ravaged%20by%20fire%20in%202019%20and%20reopened%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20restoration%20cost%20a%20total%20of%20nearly%20700%20million%20euros%20(%24730%20million)%20and%20was%20financed%20from%20the%20846%20million%20euros%20in%20donations%20that%20poured%20in%20from%20150%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMacron%20scored%20a%20major%20diplomatic%20coup%20with%20Notre%20Dame's%20renovation%20and%20reopening%2C%20and%20some%20critics%20say%20he%20is%20seeking%20to%20score%20political%20points%20with%20his%20Louvre%20announcements%20amid%20a%20protracted%20political%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20his%20field%2C%26quot%3B%20grumbled%20a%20member%20of%20the%20government.%20%26quot%3BHe's%20buying%20himself%20popularity%20points%20on%20the%20cheap.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMacron's%20popularity%20has%20dropped%20to%20a%20new%20low%20since%20his%20first%20election%20in%202017%2C%20according%20to%20a%20poll%20published%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%2021%20percent%20of%20respondents%20to%20the%20IFOP%20poll%20published%20in%20the%20Journal%20de%20Dimanche%20newspaper%20expressed%20satisfaction%20with%20the%2047-year-old%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20most%20other%20Paris%20museums%2C%20which%20are%20closed%20every%20Monday%2C%20the%20Louvre%20is%20shut%20on%20Tuesdays%2C%20meaning%20Macron%20did%20not%20cross%20paths%20with%20the%20general%20public%20on%20his%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738085220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fnj7ecqvg_mona-lisa_625x300_14_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmona-lisa-to-have-special-space-macron-unveils-plan-to-renovate-louvre-museum-7581290%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22French%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20said%20Tuesday%20that%20the%20Louvre%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bredesigned%2C%20restored%20and%20enlarged%26quot%3B%20after%20the%20director%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20visited%20museum%20voiced%20alarm%20about%20dire%20conditions%20for%20visitors%20and%20its%20collections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmona-lisa-to-have-special-space-macron-unveils-plan-to-renovate-louvre-museum-7581290%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Champions%20Trophy%20Stadiums%20In%20A%20Mess%20In%20Pakistan%2C%20ICC%20CEO%20Steps%20Down%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EInternational%20Cricket%20Council%20CEO%20Geoff%20Allardice%20has%20decided%20to%20st