istance%20provided%20directly%20to%20individuals.%26quot%3B%20That%20would%20presumably%20spare%20food%20aid%20for%20the%20poor%20and%20disability%20payments%2C%20though%20it%20was%20not%20clear%20whether%20health%20care%20programs%20for%20veterans%20and%20low-income%20people%20would%20be%20affected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20OMB%20memo%20asserted%20that%20the%20federal%20government%20spent%20nearly%20%2410%20trillion%20in%20fiscal%20year%202024%2C%20with%20more%20than%20%243%20trillion%20devoted%20to%20financial%20assistance%20such%20as%20grants%20and%20loans.%20But%20the%20source%20of%20those%20figures%20was%20not%20clear%20-%20the%20nonpartisan%20Congressional%20Budget%20Office%20estimated%20government%20spending%20in%202024%20at%20a%20much%20lower%20%246.75%20trillion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20memo%20is%20the%20latest%20directive%20in%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20campaign%20to%20dramatically%20reshape%20the%20federal%20government%2C%20the%20nation's%20largest%20employer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20blizzard%20of%20executive%20actions%20last%20week%2C%20the%20new%20president%20shuttered%20all%20diversity%20programs%2C%20imposed%20a%20hiring%20freeze%2C%20sent%20national%20security%20officials%20home%2C%20ordered%20a%20pause%20in%20foreign%20aid%20and%20sought%20to%20strip%20away%20job%20protections%20from%20thousands%20of%20civil%20servants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20spending%20freeze%20ordered%20by%20OMB%20takes%20effect%20at%205%20p.m.%20ET%20(2200%20GMT)%20on%20Tuesday.%20Agencies%20have%20until%20Feb.%2010%20to%20submit%20detailed%20information%20on%20any%20programs%20subject%20to%20the%20suspension.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDEMOCRATS%20CHALLENGE%20'UNLAWFUL'%20MOVE%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20federal%20government%20provides%20money%20to%20a%20broad%20swath%20of%20nonprofits%2C%20many%20of%20which%20reacted%20with%20dismay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20order%20is%20a%20potential%20five-alarm%20fire%20for%20nonprofit%20organizations%20and%20the%20people%20and%20communities%20they%20serve%2C%26quot%3B%20Diane%20Yentel%2C%20president%20%26amp%3B%20CEO%20of%20the%20National%20Council%20of%20Nonprofits%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BFrom%20pausing%20research%20on%20cures%20for%20childhood%20cancer%20to%20halting%20food%20assistance%2C%20safety%20from%20domestic%20violence%2C%20and%20closing%20suicide%20hotlines%2C%20the%20impact%20of%20even%20a%20short%20pause%20in%20funding%20could%20be%20devastating%20and%20cost%20lives.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemocrats%20immediately%20challenged%20Trump's%20action%20as%20unlawful%20and%20dangerous.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20letter%20to%20Vaeth%20late%20on%20Monday%2C%20U.S.%20Senator%20Patty%20Murray%20and%20U.S.%20Representative%20Rose%20DeLauro%2C%20the%20top%20Democrats%20on%20the%20congressional%20appropriation%20committees%2C%20said%20the%20order%20was%20%26quot%3Bbreathtaking%2C%20unprecedented%2C%20and%20will%20have%20devastating%20consequences%20across%20the%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20write%20today%20to%20urge%20you%20in%20the%20strongest%20possible%20terms%20to%20uphold%20the%20law%20and%20the%20Constitution%20and%20ensure%20all%20federal%20resources%20are%20delivered%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Democrats%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenate%20Democratic%20Leader%20Chuck%20Schumer%20said%20the%20administration%20did%20not%20have%20the%20authority%20to%20halt%20spending%20that%20had%20been%20approved%20by%20Congress%20and%20that%20the%20order%2C%20if%20implemented%2C%20would%20harm%20millions%20of%20Americans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20will%20mean%20missed%20payrolls%20and%20rent%20payments%20and%20everything%20in%20between%3A%20chaos%20for%20everything%20from%20universities%20to%20non-profit%20charities%2C%20state%20disaster%20assistance%2C%20local%20law%20enforcement%2C%20aid%20to%20the%20elderly%2C%20and%20food%20for%20those%20in%20need%2C%26quot%3B%20Sc