e%20he%20had%20done%20enough%20knocking%2C%20Kohli%20entered%20the%20spinners'%20nets%20where%20he%20faced%20left-arm%20spinners%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Harsh%20Tyagi%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F110583-harsh-tyagi-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHarsh%20Tyagi%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Sumit%20Mathur.%20A%20few%20balls%20did%20grip%20and%20stop%20but%20there%20wasn't%20much%20bite%20in%20their%20bowling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDitto%20for%20pacers%20Navdeep%20Saini%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Money%20Grewal%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F120085-money-grewal-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMoney%20Grewal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Rahul%20Gehlot%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Siddhant%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F108614-siddhant-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESiddhant%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20India%20nets%2C%20Kohli%20hardly%20looked%20troubled%20although%20he%20did%20practice%20leaving%20a%20lot%20of%20deliveries.%20With%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20round%20the%20corner%2C%20Kohli%20was%20seen%20trying%20to%20play%20a%20lot%20beside%20the%20line%20of%20deliveries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20late%2C%20he%20is%20concentrating%20on%20back-foot%20play%20and%20trying%20to%20increase%20his%20range%20of%20shots%20square%20of%20wicket.%20Obviously%2C%20before%20trying%20out%20in%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%20domestic%20cricket%20is%20good%20ground%20for%20a%20'Pilot%20Episode'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20was%20very%20happy%20with%20the%20surfaces.%20He%20said%2C%20practice%20wicket%2C%20centre%20strip%20everything%20is%20of%20top%20quality.%20I%20told%20him%20credit%20to%20our%20young%20curator%20Ankit%20Datta.%20He%20said%2C%20'%3Cem%3EBhaiyya%20mazaa%20aa%20gaya%20batting%20karke.%20Kal%20phir%20aaoonga%20batting%20karne%3C%2Fem%3E%2C'%20Bhati%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdvice%20for%20little%20Kabir%20and%20his%20teammates%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3