%3E.%20Kohli%2C%20who%20will%20be%20playing%20his%20first%20Ranji%20match%20since%202012%2C%20practiced%20hard%20in%20the%20nets%20as%20he%20faced%20five%20bowlers%20-%C2%A0%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Money%20Grewal%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F120085-money-grewal-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMoney%20Grewal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Navdeep%20Saini%2C%20Rahul%20Gehlot%2C%20Siddhant%20Sharma%2C%20Vivek%20Gusain%20-%20in%20a%2025-minute%20session%2C%20The%20report%20claimed%20that%20he%20looked%20confident%20but%20was%20beaten%20a%20few%20times%20by%20Saini%20and%20Sharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Virat%20spent%20almost%20half%20an%20hour%20facing%203%20spinners%20-%C2%A0%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Harsh%20Tyagi%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F110583-harsh-tyagi-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHarsh%20Tyagi%3C%2Fa%3E%20(left-arm)%2C%20Sumit%20Mathur%20(left-arm)%2C%20and%20Shivam%20(right-arm).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20an%20'intense'%20practice%20session%20for%20the%20star%20who%20did%20not%20have%20a%20good%20outing%20in%20Australia%20and%20although%20he%20did%20not%20face%20much%20issues%2C%20Virat%20was%20beaten%20twice%20by%20Tyagi's%20sharp%20spin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20exactly%209am%20when%20his%20jet%20black%20Porsche%20zoomed%20in%20through%20the%20Feroz%20Shah%20Kotla%20ground's%20'%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virender%20Sehwag%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F86-virender-sehwag-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirender%20Sehwag%3C%2Fa%3E%20Gate'%2C%20it%20was%20homecoming%20for%20Delhi's%20very%20own%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20who%20checked%20in%20for%20a%20training%20stint%20with%20his%20first-class%20team%20after%20more%20than%2012%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESave%20for%20pacer%20Navdeep%20Saini%2C%20all%20other%2018%20members%20of%20Delhi's%20squad%20had%20only%20seen%20him%20on%20TV%20and%20grown%20up%20listening%20to%20the%20tales%20of%20how%20'Cheeku'%2C%20the%20cherubic%20tale