p-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20team%20that%20represented%20India%20at%20the%20FIRST%20Global%20Challenge%20in%20Geneva%2C%20securing%20the%2029th%20rank%20out%20of%20167%20countries!%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20their%20success%20in%20the%20FTC%2C%20the%20team%20of%20about%20five%20children%20were%20selected%20to%20represent%20India%20at%20the%20First%20Global%20Challenge%20in%202022%2C%20an%20international%20robotics%20competition%20held%20in%20Switzerland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20parents%20had%20so%20many%20questions%20when%20I%20told%20them%20we%20would%20be%20taking%20their%20children%20to%20Switzerland.%20They%20were%20daily%20wage%20earners%2C%20with%20no%20passports%20or%20experience%20with%20international%20travel%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20to%20convince%20them%20that%20the%20kids%20were%20safe%20and%20that%20they%20were%20chosen%20for%20a%20reason.%20It%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20easy%2C%20but%20we%20made%20it%20work.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20emotional%20moments%20came%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20competition%2C%20when%20everyone%20gathered%20to%20see%20the%20children%20off.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20parents%2C%20an%20auto-rickshaw%20driver%2C%20told%20me%20that%20he%20drives%20to%20the%20airport%20every%20day%20to%20drop%20passengers%2C%20but%20never%20imagined%20he%20would%20one%20day%20be%20dropping%20his%20own%20son%20off%20for%20an%20international%20flight%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20founder%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20800px)%20100vw%2C%20800px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-01-14-at-16.47.01-1737182662.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22For%20government%20school%20children%2C%20TIS%20has%20launched%20Project%20Udaan%2C%20pathways%20for%20engineering%