ospital%2C%20he%20was%20so%20impressed%20by%20its%20potential%20that%20he%20expressed%20interest%20in%20customising%20it%20further%20to%20make%20the%20solution%20even%20more%20practical%20and%20effective%20for%20the%20hospital%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20story%20that%20the%20founder%20shares%20is%20that%20of%20a%20class%2011%20student%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20Kathak%20dancer.%20%E2%80%9CRealising%20that%20deaf%20children%20struggle%20to%20connect%20with%20music%2C%20she%20invented%20a%20wristband%20that%20tracks%20sound%20waves%20and%20converts%20them%20into%20vibrations.%20This%20allows%20the%20wearer%20to%20dance%20along%20with%20the%20beats%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20government%20school%20children%2C%20TIS%20has%20launched%20Project%20Udaan%2C%20pathways%20for%20engineering.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20designed%20for%20students%20of%20classes%205%20to%2012.%20The%20programme%20starts%20by%20laying%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F292528%2Fengineer-shoaib-dar-started-pi-jam-foundation-to-provide-free-computer-coding-to-rural-kids%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estrong%20foundation%20in%20digital%20literacy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20communication%2C%20and%20mathematical%20skills.%20Then%2C%20we%20gradually%20build%20on%20these%20with%20problem-solving%20techniques%2C%20an%20introduction%20to%20robotics%20through%20hands-on%20learning%2C%20and%20eventually%20a%20course%20on%20web%20app%20development%2C%E2%80%9D%20Meenal%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESuccessful%20impact%20and%20future%20growth%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20work%20with%20both%20private%20and%20government%20school%20children%20because%20they%20have%20so%20much%20to%20learn%20from%20each%20other.%20At%20our%20TIS%20centres%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20Bengaluru%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20truly%20heartwarming%20to%20watch%20them%20interact%20and%20collaborate%20so%20beautifully.%