0neglect%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20not%20free%20before%20marriage%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20reflects.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20first%20time%2C%20I%20felt%20I%20could%20explore%20the%20world.%20My%20husband%20encouraged%20me%20to%20do%20what%20I%20wanted%20%E2%80%94%20read%2C%20work%2C%20and%20question%20the%20world%20around%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20512px)%20100vw%2C%20512px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Funnamed-4-1737634066.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kalpana%20continues%20to%20collaborate%20with%20various%20organisations%20to%20ensure%20no%20woman%20is%20left%20malnourished%20%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Funnamed-4-1737634066.jpg%20512w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Funnamed-4-1737634066-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Funnamed-4-1737634066-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Funnamed-4-1737634066-400x300.jpg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Funnamed-4-1737634066-200x150.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Funnamed-4-1737634066-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-400236%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22384%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKalpana%20continues%20to%20collaborate%20with%20various%20organisations%20to%20ensure%20no%20woman%20is%20left%20malnourished%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20nothing%20could%20stop%20her.%20She%20continued%20to%20visit%20rural%20areas%2C%20distributing%20essential%20items%2C%20sanitisers%20and%20masks